chart_description: This chart displays a summary of the pause duration of garbage collection cycles in seconds. It helps identify how long the garbage collection process takes and if it may be impacting latency or performance.

dimension_descriptions.quantile_0: The minimum pause duration for the garbage collection process.
dimension_descriptions.quantile_0.25: 25% of the pause duration values for garbage collection cycles fall below this value.
dimension_descriptions.quantile_0.5: 50% of the pause duration values for garbage collection cycles fall below this value.
dimension_descriptions.quantile_0.75: 75% of the pause duration values for garbage collection cycles fall below this value.
dimension_descriptions.quantile_1: The maximum pause duration for the garbage collection process.
